parameters:
Konoha-sama, have you been speaking differently
lately? I'm always available to practice
swordsmanship with you.
The castle seems a bit busy. Did something happen?
~The Hero of Disodart~ Priest Muramasa Rests Here
Father... I've had an unbelievable experience...

I hope that such things won't happen again in the
future...

Well then, I should get back to my duties as a
shrine maiden... Ahh~ But being a magical girl was
also quite interesting, you know.

It would be fun if I could use that power here,
for sure, just kidding.
Lord Konoha!!!! This is a major crisis!!!!

I wonder what it is~? I won't be surprised by
something trivial.

A horde of monsters is attacking from outside the
town...!
Haa~?! Geez, there's no helping it!
Leave it to Magical Girl Konoha!

\C[2] You can select New Game+ option.※ If you
don't select it here, you can also start New Game+
from Tower of Reincarnation 2F.
